to update quartz run
`git remote -v`
`git remote add upstream https://github.com/jackyzha0/quartz.git`
`git pull upsteam LATEST_BRANCHA` and you might need the `--allow-unrelated-histories` flag

to push a new version of the site simply push to main. ci is done using cloudflare and github pages.

This was set using these pages as reference:
https://quartz.jzhao.xyz/setting-up-your-GitHub-repository
https://quartz.jzhao.xyz/hosting

